Metadata.Title: FIVE GUYS
Metadata.Description: I've found for you the Five Guys. Those five mercenaries are the ones whose have killed all these womens back in Libia. It's time to return them the favor. I've setup your equipment for this mission. You'll begin in the sanctuary in mendoza, on the cliff. Take on your TACTICAL SUIT to be able to leave the area by the sea. Take with you a SILENT PISTOL for cameras, a TACTICAL KNIFE and a HOOK for the door.I leave you to prepare.K.
